{"tid":2407582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：「愛國運動才剛開始。」","createTime":"2021-02-14T06:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T13:03:29.000Z","uid":318316,"like":435,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"65f34ec5dd667fb93a57d559faea884c68e2856e","tid":2407582,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"特朗普對參院的否決投票發表聲明，譴責該審理是「歷史上最大的獵巫行動。」<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，將致力讓「美國再次偉大」的政治行動「才剛開始」。 <br />\n<br />\n眾議院議長裴洛西（Nancy Pelosi）則抨擊對此案投下無罪票的共和黨籍參議員「懦弱」。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/430C/production/_116946171_whatsubject.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F800%2Fcpsprodpb%2F430C%2Fproduction%2F_116946171_whatsubject.jpg&h=3ceafef0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n特朗普再次從被美國參議院的定罪中全身而退。因為他的共和黨人同事基本上都站在他那邊。最終的投票結果是57-43，還差10票才能到達到能判他有罪的2/3票數。<br />\n<br />\n從最基本的角度來看，這是這位前總統的一次勝利。<br />\n<br />\n如果他有意願，特朗普仍然有資格在2024年再次競選總統。<br />\n<strong><br />\n所有跡象表明，支持他的陣營基本上仍然完好。無論是在眾議院還是在參議院，大多數共和黨公職人員都下反對彈劾票。而那些支持彈劾的共和黨，已經面臨著猛烈的抨擊，而且一些人還是遭到共和黨同志的正式譴責。<br />\n<br />\n這位前總統在新聞稿上慶祝了他的無罪並譴責民主黨，同時表示他的政治運動才剛剛開始。 </strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-56059274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-56059274&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=828e91bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-56059274&h=170eca7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-56059274</a>"},{"pid":"82bb466fb5a9eff11eee3ad1253b29ec9913019e","tid":2407582,"uid":370061,"like":57,"dislike":4,"score":53,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T07:04:51.000Z","msg":"睇錯回憶小子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a9ed799c62059f11c8c2f13edba30f467c0387","tid":2407582,"uid":266503,"like":142,"dislike":3,"score":139,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T07:06:04.000Z","m